(19556, 'Gapsolox 150mg 10 caps.', 'جابسولوكس 150 مجم 10 كبسولات', '', '32', 'Pregabalin', 'Spimaco misr', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', '', 'Anti-epileptic.gaba analogs', '150mg', 'Pregabalin is indicated for the management of neuropathic pain associated with diabetic peripheral neuropathy, postherpetic neuralgia, fibromyalgia, neuropathic pain associated with spinal cord injury, and as adjunctive therapy for the treatment of partial-onset seizures in patients 1 month of age and older.[L7066]', '', '', 790, '2022-07-12', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
